{"type":null,"faqId":43423,"title":"通话过程中手机黑屏","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>这是正常现象。手机靠近头部时，听筒附近的接近光传感器被遮挡，屏幕自动关闭防止误操作。手机离开头部后，屏幕自动点亮。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>为了保证手机的正常使用，请不要用手机套或其他物体遮挡听筒附近的屏幕。给手机贴膜时，注意避开接近光感应器，某些透光性较差的贴膜会造成接近光失效。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8924","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442398846000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":4,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"通话,手机,黑屏","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}